#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today’s lesson is about giving instructions that work!\n"
"How we give instructions matters – children are more likely to listen when we say what we want them to do, not what not to do.\n"
"Instead of “Don’t touch that!”, try: “Please only touch things that belong to us.”"
msgstr ""
"Isifundo sanamhlanje singokunika imiyalelo esebenzayo!\n"
"Indlela esinikeza ngayo imiyalelo ibalulekile - abantwana bamamela kakhulu xa sisithi sifuna benze ntoni, kunaxa sisithi mabangenzi lonto.\n"
"Endaweni yokuba \"sukubamba lonto!\", zama: \" Ndicela ubambe izinto ezi zezethu qha.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tap play to learn how giving positive instructions can help you and your family"
msgstr "Cofa dlala ukufunda ukuba ukunikeza ngemiyalelo elungileyo kungakunceda njani wena kunye nosapho lwakho"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings everyone.\n"
"\n"
"Let’s try something: Don’t think about a pink elephant…\n"
"What did you think about? A pink elephant?\n"
"\n"
"The same happens when we give negative instructions to our children. When we tell them “stop fighting” or “stop playing with your food”, they don’t know how to think about what we DO want them to do, only what we DON’T want them to do.”\n"
"\n"
"When you give a positive instruction, your child is more likely to follow it."
msgstr ""
"Molweni nonke\n"
"\n"
"Makhe sizame into: Sukucinga ngendlovu epinki...\n"
"Ucinga ngantoni? Nge ndlovu epinki?\n"
"\n"
"Kwenzeka into efanayo xa sinika imiyalelo engalunganga ebantwaneni bethu. Xa sisithi' mabayeke ukulwa \"ókanye yekani udlala ngokutya kwenu'. Abayazi indlela yokucinga ngalento SIFUNA ukuba bayenze, kuphela into ESINGAFUNI ukuba bayenze.\n"
"\n"
"Xa unika imiyalelo eylungileyo, kunokwenzeka ukuba umntwana ayilandele."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name:
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let’s see how @data.characters.f1_father.name gives instructions to @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name:"
msgstr "Makhe sibone ukuba u @data.characters.f1_father.name uyinike njani inimiyalelo ku@data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name:"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name is playing with the blocks on the floor."
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name udlala ngebloko phantsi."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It looks like you’re having a lot of fun, @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name. It’s almost time to clean up. In 3 minutes, please put your blocks away."
msgstr "Kubonakala ngathi uyonwaba kakhulu u@data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name.Selisondele ixesha lokucoca,kwimizuzu emi 3 nceda ubeke iibloko zakho ecaleni."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "*3 minutes later*"
msgstr "* Emva kwemizuzu e- 3 *"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "3 minutes are over, @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name. Please pack away your blocks."
msgstr "Imizuzu emi- 3 iphelile @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name Nceda upakishe ibloko zakho ecaleni."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Okay."
msgstr "Kulungile."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thank you very much for packing away the blocks when I asked you, @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name. Because you listened so well, I will read you an extra story before bed."
msgstr "Enkosi kakhulu ngokupakisha kude iibloks xa ndikucelile, @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name. Kuba umamele kakuhle, ndizokufundela ibali elongezelelekileyo phambi kokuba ulale."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yay!"
msgstr "Yay!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Once upon a time…"
msgstr "Ngaminazana ithile…"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let’s reflect on what we can learn from @data.characters.f1_father.name and his daughter, @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name."
msgstr "Makhe sijonge ukuba sinokufunda ntoni na ku@data.characters.f1_father.name kunye nentombi yakhe, u@data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"@data.characters.f1_father.name did a few things to help his daughter follow instructions:\n"
"\n"
"- 🤝🏾 Connect with @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name by saying her name and praising her, BEFORE giving an instruction\n"
"- 🗺️ Give one instruction at a time\n"
"- ⚠️ Give a transition warning (_\"in 3 minutes, please put your blocks away\"_) \n"
"- 📘 Follow through with a positive consequence (read an extra story)"
msgstr ""
"U@data.characters.f1_father.name wenze izinto ezimbalwa ukunceda intombi yakhe ukulandela imiyalelo\n"
"\n"
"- 🤝🏾 Qhangamshelana no@data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name ngokubiza igama lakhe okanye umncome, PHAMBI kokuba umnike umyalelo\n"
"-🗺️Nika umyalelo ubemnye ngexesha\n"
"- ⚠️Nika isilumkiso senguqu (- \"ngemizuzu e 3, nceda ubeke ibhokisi zakho kude\"-)\n"
"- 📘Landela ngesiphumo esihle ( funda ibali elongezelekileyo)"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What steps does @data.characters.f1_father.name take to help @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name follow her instruction?"
msgstr "Ngawaphi amanyathelo u@data.characters.f1_father.name awathathileyo ukunceda u@data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name alandele imiyalelo yakhe?"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He warns @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name that misbehaviour is not acceptable"
msgstr "Ulumkisa u@data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name ukuba ukuziphatha kakubi akwamkelekanga"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Try again! @data.characters.f1_father.name actually gives a positive instruction by telling @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name what she should do rather than shouldn’t do. This will help @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name to follow the instruction."
msgstr "Zama kwakhona! u@data.characters.f1_father.name eneneni unika imiyalelo ayakhayo ngokuxelela u@data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name into emakayenze nokuba ingayenzi.Oku kuyakunceda u@data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name ukuba alandele umyalelo."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He gives @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name a transition warning and follows through with what he said"
msgstr "Unike u@data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name isilumkiso esinenguqu kwaye alandele oko akuthethileyo"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name’s
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Correct! These steps make it more likely that @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name follows @data.characters.f1_father.name’s instruction. He also praises his daughter."
msgstr "Unyanisile! La manyathelo enza ukuba u@data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name alandele kakuhle kakhulu imiyalelo ka@data.characters.f1_father.name. Kwaye uyayincoma intombi yakhe."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He makes @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name feel guilty for taking too long"
msgstr "Wenza u@data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name azive enetyla ngokuthatha ixesha elide"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Try again! Making her feel guilty will make @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name less motivated to follow instructions both now and in the future. It will also feel stressful for @data.characters.f1_father.name."
msgstr "Zama kwakhona! ukumenza azive enetyala u@data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name kungamenza akhuthazeke kancinci ukulandela imiyalelo ngoku kunye nakwixesha elizayo. Uyakuziva kwakhona enoxinzelelo ngenxa ka@data.characters.f1_father.name."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He tells her to stop playing and start cleaning"
msgstr "Umxelele ukuba makayeke ukudlala kwaye aqale ukucoca"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Try again! He gives @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name a positive instruction to “clean up” without giving a negative one of “stop playing.”"
msgstr "Zama kwakhona! unike u@data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name umyalelo owakhayo ukuba ''coca'' ngaphandle kokumnika ongakhiyo ''yeka ukudlala''."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"We saw that @data.characters.f1_father.name first connected with his daughter by saying her name, getting down to her level, and giving her praise. This put him in the best position to then give @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name an instruction.\n"
"\n"
"Let's think about what would happen if things went differently."
msgstr ""
"Siyibonile lonto u@data.characters.f1_father.name uqale waqhagamshelana nentombi yakhe ngokuyibiza ngegama layo, wehlela phantsi kwinqanaba layo, kwaye wayincoma.Oku kumbeka kwindwo engcono ukuze anike u@data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name umyalelo.\n"
"\n"
"Masicinge ngento ibinokwenzeka xa izinto bezihambe ngokwahlukileyo."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      “@data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name,
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What would have happened if @data.characters.f1_father.name had said: “@data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name, stop playing with your blocks, and don’t go to bed with dirty teeth!”"
msgstr "Yintoni ibinokwenzeka ukuba u@data.characters.f1_father.name ebethe: \"@data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name, yeka ukudlala ngebhokisi zakho, kwaye ungalali unamaziyo amdaka!''"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name could feel confused or overwhelmed"
msgstr "U@data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name angaziva ebhidekile okanye imongamele"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Exactly. It is important to give one positive instruction at a time. It makes a big difference."
msgstr "Ngokuchanekileyo! Kubalulekile ukunika umyalelo owakhayo ubemnye ngexesha. Oku kungenza umahluko omkhulu."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name would respect her father's authority"
msgstr "U@data.characters.f1_daughter_2.name uyakulihlonipha igunya likatata wakhe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Try again! It’s important to give one positive instruction at a time. This will make the instruction easier to follow."
msgstr "Zama kwakhona! Kubalulekile ukunika umyalelo owakhaya ubemnye ngexesha. Oku kuyakwenza umyalelo ubelula ukuwulandela."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let’s look at another family to see how positive instructions can help to prevent problems before they start!"
msgstr "Makhe sijonge kwelinye usapho ukuba imiyalelo elungileyo inganceda njani ukwenza ingxaki zingabikho phambi kokuba ziqale!"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name
#.      @data.characters.f2_daughter_3.name,
#.      @data.characters.f2_son_8.name,
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f2_grandfather.name is working in the garden while his granddaughter, @data.characters.f2_daughter_3.name, and grandson, @data.characters.f2_son_8.name, are playing with a ball:"
msgstr "U@data.characters.f2_grandfather.name usebenza egadini ngexesha umzukulwana wakhe oyintombazana, u@data.characters.f2_daughter_3.name, kunye nomzukulwana oyinkwenkwe, u@data.characters.f2_son_8.name, badlala ngebhola:"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Give it back to me!"
msgstr "Yibuyisele kum!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "But I want it!"
msgstr "Kodwa ndiyayifuna!"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f2_daughter_3.name
#.      @data.characters.f2_son_8.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f2_daughter_3.name and @data.characters.f2_son_8.name come and help me plant these vegetables together."
msgstr "U@data.characters.f2_daughter_3.name kunye no@data.characters.f2_son_8.name izani nizokundincedisa sityale imifuno kunye."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thank you for coming to help me. We are going to grow lots of delicious vegetables together."
msgstr "Enkosi ngokuba nize uzokundincedisa. Sizakulima imifuno emininzi emnandi kunye."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let’s reflect on what @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name did here."
msgstr "Makhe sijonge ukuba u@data.characters.f2_grandfather.name wenze ntoni apha."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What does @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name do to prevent the argument from getting out of hand?"
msgstr "Wenze ntoni u@data.characters.f2_grandfather.name ukuthintela ukuba ingxabano ingaphumi izandla?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He involves them in a positive activity and gives them praise"
msgstr "Uye wababandakanya kumdlalo omhle kwaye wabancoma"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That’s right. He quickly intervenes to distract them, and gives a positive instruction to redirect them to a positive behaviour."
msgstr "Kulungile. Uye wangenelela ngokukhawleza ukubaphazamisa, kwaye uye wabanika umyalelo olungileyo ukubaqondisa kwindlela yokuziphatha eyiyo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He reminds them it’s important to get along"
msgstr "Uye wabakhumbuza ukuba kubalulekile ukuvana"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He gives them a warning for a consequence"
msgstr "Uye wabanika isilumkiso semiphumela"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Try again! @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name gives the children a positive instruction to redirect them to a positive behaviour."
msgstr "Zama kwakhona! u@data.characters.f2_grandfather.name unike abantwana umyalelo olungileyo ukubaqondisa kwindlela yokuziphatha elungileyo."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What would have happened if @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name had not paid attention to the children?"
msgstr "Bekunikwenzeka ntoni ukuba u@data.characters.f2_grandfather.name ebengabahoyanga abantwana?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "They would have continued to argue"
msgstr "Ngebeqhubekekile ukuba baxoxe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Yes. The situation between the children would have gotten out of hand. \n"
"These are all correct answers!"
msgstr ""
"Ewe. Imeko phakathi kwabantwana ngeyayi phumele ngapha kwezandla. \n"
"Zonke ezimpendulo ziyinyani!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "They could have hurt each other in the argument"
msgstr "Ngebeye bonzakalisana engxoxweni"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Yes. The children could have gotten so upset that they would have hurt each other. \n"
"These are all correct answers!"
msgstr ""
"Ewe. Abantwana bebezakukhathazeka ukuba bebeye bonzakalisana.\n"
"Zonke ezimpendulo zilungile!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f2_grandfather.name would have had to stop working in the garden"
msgstr "u@data.characters.f2_grandfather.name ebezakubanqanda ukusebenza egadini"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Yes. If @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name had kept quiet, he would have had to spend more time and energy trying to resolve the conflict. \n"
"These are all correct answers!"
msgstr ""
"Ewe. Ukuba u@data.characters.f2_grandfather.name ebethule, ebezakuchitha ixesha elininzi kunye namandla ezama ukusombulula umlo.\n"
"Zonke ezimpendulo zilungile!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are three tips to give positive instructions that work."
msgstr "Nazi iingcebiso ezintathu ukunikeza imiyalelo elungileyo emsebenzini."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "BE SPECIFIC"
msgstr "CACISA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say the behaviour you want your child to do.\n"
"But before you do that, connect to them, so they are more likely to listen."
msgstr ""
"Xela indlela yokuziphatha ofuna umntwana wakho ayenze.\n"
"Kodwa phambi kokuba uqale, qhagamshelana nabo, bavamile kakhulu ukuba bamamele."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Use your child’s name to get their attention. Go down to their level. Make eye contact.\n"
"\n"
"Then say exactly what you want them to do. For example: “Please take your shoes off when you come inside, dear”."
msgstr ""
"Sebenzisa igama lomntwana wakho ukufumana ingqalelo kuye. Yehlela ezantsi kwizinga lwakhe. Yenza uqhagamshelwano lwamehlo.\n"
"\n"
"Emva koko chaza into ofuna ukuba ayenze. Umzekelo: \" Nceda ukhulule izihlangu zakho xa ungena ngaphakathiu, sithandwa\"."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "BE REALISTIC"
msgstr "YIBA SENGQIQWENI"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Give one instruction at a time, and make sure that the instruction is something that your child can do."
msgstr "Nika umyalelo ubemnye ngexesha, kwaye qiniseka ukuba umyalelo yinto umntwana wakho anokwazi ukuyenza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Giving a transition warning helps when you are asking them to change activities! For example: “In 10 minutes, you will need to pack away your toys so we can start getting ready for bed.”"
msgstr "Ukunikeza ngesilumkiso esinenguqu kuyanceda xa ubaumcela ukuba atshimtshe imidlalo! Umzekelo: \" kwimizuzu eyi 10, Kuzofuneka uqoqoshe izinto zakho zokudlala sizokwazi ukulungela ukulala.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "BE POSITIVE"
msgstr "YIBA NESIMO SENGQONDO ESIHLE"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Try using positive words when giving instructions. For example, instead of “Don’t shout inside”, say “Talk in a quiet voice when we’re inside.” \n"
"\n"
"ALWAYS praise your child immediately when they follow your instruction. This will make them more likely to repeat the behaviour and listen to you next time!"
msgstr ""
"Zama ukusebenzisa amagama akwisimo esihle xa unikisa ngemiyalelo. Umzekelo, ebdaweni yokuba \" sukungxola ngaphakathi\", yithi \" thetha ngelizwi elithuleyo xa singaphakathi.\"\n"
"\n"
"Maxa wonke ncoma umntwana wakho ngoko nangoko xa elandele umyalelo wakho. Lonto izakumenza avamise ukuphinda indlela yokuziphatha kwaye akumamele kwixesha elizayo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "More"
msgstr "Okuninzi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Give instructions in a firm voice and stay calm. Behave as if you expect your child to do what you ask.\n"
"\n"
"Also, be kind to yourself if you forget sometimes. Learning how to give positive instructions is not easy, but it works!"
msgstr ""
"Nika imiyalelo ngelizwi eloqinileyo kwaye uhlale uzolile. Ziphathe ngendlela okungathi ulindele umntwana wakho enze into oyicelayo.\n"
"\n"
"Kwaye, yibanenceba kuwe xa uye walibala ngamanye amaxesha. Ukufunda ukunikeza imiyalelo emihle akukho lula, kodwa kuyasebenza!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "To practise giving instructions that work, let's try turning our negative instructions into positive ones."
msgstr "Ukuziqhelanisa nokunikeza imiyalelo kuyasebenza, masizame ukuguqula imiyalelo yethu emibi kwizinto ezintle."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Select each option to see how to turn it into a positive instruction:"
msgstr "Khetha ukhetho lubelunye ubone ukuba ukuguqula njani libe kwimeko entle yomyalelo:"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "🧸 Stop fighting with your siblings over toys!"
msgstr "🧸 Yeka ukulwa nabantwana bakowenu ngezinto zokudlala!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Try saying something like “Please take turns with toys! Each of you can have 5 minutes.”"
msgstr "Zama ukuthetha into efana \" Ndicela nitshintshisane ngezinto zokudlala! Ngamnye kuni anagabanemizuzu emi 5.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "🗣️ No shouting in the house!"
msgstr "🗣️ Hayi akukhwazwa endlini!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Try saying something like “Please speak with a quiet, indoor voice.”"
msgstr "Zama into efana \"Nceda uthethe ngelizwi elizolileyo, langaphakathi.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "🍅 Stop throwing food!"
msgstr "🍅 Yeka ukulahla ukutya!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Try saying something like “Please keep your food on the plate.”"
msgstr "Zama into efana \" Nceda ugcine ukutya kwakho epleyitini.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "🖍️ Don't write on the walls!"
msgstr "🖍️ Sukubhala emadongeni!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Try saying something like “Please only write on paper.”"
msgstr "Zama ukuthetha into efana \" Nceda ubhale ephepheni kuphela.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Ready to give it a go? This week's home activity is to give your child specific, realistic, and positive instructions. \n"
"\n"
"Remember to give one instruction at a time and praise them. This will help your child to follow your instructions."
msgstr ""
"Ukulungele ukuyenza! Umsebenzi wasekhaya waleveki kukunika umntwana wakho umyalelo ocacileyo, osengqiqweni, kwaye owakhayo.\n"
"\n"
"Khumbula ukunika umyalelo omnye ngexesha kwaye umncome. Oku kuyakunceda umntwana wakho ukuba alandele imiyalelo yakho."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_3.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hear how @data.characters.media_female_3.name learned to give her children positive instructions"
msgstr "Yiva ukuba u@data.characters.media_female_3.name wenze njani ukufunda ukunika abantwana bakhe imiyalelo eyakhayo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Before, I used to raise my children the way I was raised: I would tell them “don’t do this, don’t do that.” We used to fight a lot, but things have really changed when I learned about giving positive instructions.\n"
"\n"
"Now I focus on the behaviour I want to see, and give clear and simple instructions to my children. It took time to learn to say “please do this” instead of “ don’t do this.” \n"
"My children and even my husband tell me that they love this way of doing things, because now they know what needs to be done. My child said one day “I really love this new mom,” and my own stress levels have come down a lot."
msgstr ""
"Ngaphambili, ndandibakhulisa abantwana bam ngendlela endakhuliswa ngayo: Ndandibaxelela ukuba \"musa ukuyenza lena, sukuyenza leya.\" Sasikade sisilwa, kodwa izinto ziye zatshintsha ngokwenene xa ndafunda ngokunikela imiyalelo eyakhayo.\n"
"\n"
"Ngoku ndigxile kwindlela yokuziphatha endifuna ukuyibona, kwaye ndinike imiyalelo ecacileyo nelula ebantwaneni bam. Ithathe ixesha ukufunda ukuthi \"ndicela wenze lento\" endaweni yokuba \"ungayenzi lento.\"\n"
"Abantwana bam kunye nomyeni wam bandixelele ukuba lendlela yokwenza izinto, kuba ngoku bayayazi into ekufuneka yenziwe. Umntwana ngenye imini uthe \" ndiyamthanda ngokwenene lo mama mtsha,\" kwaye nolwam uxinzelelo lwehle kakhulu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Your home activity is to give your child positive instructions. Can you do it?"
msgstr "Umsebenzi wakho wasekhaya kukunika umntwana wakho imiyalelo eyakhaya. Ungayenza lonto?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Ewe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That’s great! It might feel a bit awkward at first, but the more you try, the easier it gets. Keep up the excellent effort!"
msgstr "Kulungile! Ingavakala ingaqhelekanga ekuqaleni, kodwa ngakumbi uzama, kukhona ibalula. Qhubeka nmzamo obalaseleyo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr "Ndicinga njalo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It can take some practice, but small changes in how we speak make a big difference. Give it a try – you can do this!"
msgstr "Ingathatha ixeshana lokuziqhelanisa, kodwa utshintsho oluncinci kwindlela esithetha ngayo lwenza umahluko omkhulu. Yizame- ungayenza lento!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr "Hayi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's okay. It may take time to learn how to do this. After the next instruction you give your child, stop and think how it could be rephrased as a positive instruction. You’ve got this!"
msgstr "Kulungile. Kungathatha ixesha ukufunda ukuba kwenziwa njani oku. Emva komyalelo olandelayo owunika umntwana wakho, yima kwaye ucinge ukuba inokuphinda iphinde ichazwe njengomyalelo owakhayo. Unayo le!"

